metadata.description:
They are very first. They are very special. 

This drop features a unique NFTs that showcase one-of-a-kind fashion style of the humanoid species. Each NFT portrays a different member of the species, with their own distinctive personality and fashion sense.

These high-fashion looks are carefully crafted with elements from different universes, creating a fusion of styles that is truly unique to the collection. 

Get ready to step into the exciting world of "Hype Beasts" and make a statement with these exclusive solutions.
